&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Sublime Text&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#39;/blog/medias/img/gdipp-sublimetext-off.png&#39;&gt;&lt;img alt=&#39;Sublime Text without gdipp&#39; src=&#39;/blog/medias/img/gdipp-sublimetext-off.png&#39; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;em&gt;Without gdipp&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#39;/blog/medias/img/gdipp-sublimetext-on.png&#39;&gt;&lt;img alt=&#39;Sublime Text with gdipp&#39; src=&#39;/blog/medias/img/gdipp-sublimetext-on.png&#39; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;em&gt;With gdipp&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
